web_snippets: Dairon Blanco LaMadrid (born April 26, 1993) is a Cuban professional baseball outfielder for the Kansas City Royals of Major League Baseball (MLB).
Dairon Blanco Bio. Fullname: Dairon Blanco; Born: 4/26/1993 in Florida, Cuba ... Kansas City Royals optioned CF Dairon Blanco to Omaha Storm Chasers.
Kansas City Royals selected the contract of CF Dairon Blanco from Omaha Storm Chasers. January 12, 2023, Tigres del Licey activated CF Dairon Blanco.
